name: Doom 2's : Consumed earth
description: A continuation epidode for doom2, there were supposed to be 10 maps, but contributers were few, so there are 7 maps instead. In this mapset you're going through earth's ruins to get home on the computer to call the rescue marines to get you out of this wasted zone, to get on a helicopter and land in a place where the rest of the human population takes place.
